text: pitabrakd nasa puok del ban rtkech nowknongchamnaom puok anak now thngai del krom teangpir ban chuobaknea( now samorphoumi aou ho t) ku shai t n ban ausateanh puokke daoysaarte tongveu muoychamnuon del puok ke ban br pru td . te a l laoh pitchea ban athyeasry aoy puokke . pitabrakd nasa a l laoh mha aphytosa mha atthmot
